 {
  "text": "Good morning! This is the Central Station. The train to the city center leaves from platform two. The next train comes in five minutes. Please do not run. To go to the buses, take the stairs and turn right. To buy a ticket, go straight to the green machine near the door. Have a good trip!",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a11_listening_station.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Every day I go to work by train. First, I walk to the station near my home. I buy a ticket and I wait on platform one. The train comes and I get on. After four stops, I get off and I walk straight for two minutes. Then I turn left and my office is there. It is easy and fast.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a11_listening_my_way_to_work.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Estephano walks to the station. He buys a ticket. He gets on the train. He gets off after three stops. He turns left and finds the office.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a11_order_journey.mp3"
